<BlogPost
  title="Why Hiding Like Counts Might Actually Help Your Mental Health"
  description="There's research on this. Instagram's own internal team ran the study, and the findings were uncomfortable enough that they sat on them. Here's what the data shows about metrics and self-image."
  publishDate="2026-03-21"
